#

Linguine with Cherry Tomato and Garlic

25 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyPastaItalian

Description

A simple yet flavorful pasta dish featuring fresh cherry tomatoes and garlic, perfect for a quick dinner.

Ingredients

  • linguine pasta: 8 ounces
  • cherry tomatoes: 2 cups
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
